web app
music trial

secured db for pro and light users
encrypted sign up for pro users
 sign up for light users form: full name(min 10 chars, max 50 chars), user(min 5 chars, max 10 chars), passw, repeat passw(verify if the same), address(not null), phone(not null)

after sign up menu tabs: listen, playlists, genres, artists
pop-up message to upgrade to pro
 max songs to play untill pop- up appears: 15 (counter per played songs)
